        with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Hasbro, Inc. MONOPOLY&reg; is a trademark of Hasbro. The app is free to use.
    </div>

    <p>
        These Terms of Service ("Terms") are an agreement between you and @RuleDictionary.GameName ("we", "us"),
        operated by <a href="@publisherUrl" target="_blank" rel="noopener">JC Foundry</a>. By creating an account or
        using the app, you agree to these Terms and to our
        <a asp-area="" asp-page="/Privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. If you do not agree, please do not use the app.
    </p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">1. Who can use the app</h2>
    <p>
        You must be at least 13 years old to use @RuleDictionary.GameName. By using it you confirm that you are 13 or
        older and that the information you give us is accurate. If you are using the app somewhere that sets a higher
        minimum age for online services, you must meet that age.
    </p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">2. The service</h2>
    <p>
        @RuleDictionary.GameName is a free companion app for a physical, house-ruled tabletop game — it keeps track of
        money, cards, properties, and turns while you play on a real board. It does not involve real money, real prizes,
        or gambling of any kind; all in-game currency and assets are fictional and have no monetary value. The app is
        provided free of charge, "as is", and may be changed, limited, suspended, or withdrawn at any time.
    </p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">3. Your account</h2>
